survey_response.review_text: I had severe pain in two of my wisdom teeth which were decayed. I was too scared to go for a treatment since the other Dentists who I consulted, stated that the extraction of wisdom tooth is very complicated and may require jaw bone surgery if required; additionally, they were also charging me a fortune for the extraction. I finally re-visited Partha Dental Clinic in Jayanagar ( my first visit was last year for a dental bridge fixture) and was delighted to see Dr. Sujatha who had treated me earlier. She was very friendly and also remembered me very well. After my dental check-up and X-ray, she offered to treat it immediately (I was taken aback as I was prepared a for a couple of visits to and fro to the dental clinic with the experience from other dentists). She explained the entire procedure and made me  comfortable before the treatment.  I received a very painless and prompt treatment on the same day for the expense as less as half of what I was quoted by other dental clinics. I strongly recommend Dr. Sujatha for any dental issues.

Dr. Sujatha is very kind, interactive and acts very patiently while listening to the patient. I had already undergone root canal 3 months back which was so pathetic that the Dr left cotton inside my tooth. I consulted Dr. Sujatha coz of frequent pain and she agreed to treat me on that. I had no difficulty or pain at all even without anaesthesia, earlier when I had undergone the treatment there was hell lot of pain. She is very friendly and well experienced Doc. Very happy with the treatment and grateful to her. Overall Very much satisfied with the treatment.

I was looking for dental clinics in my neighbourhood for my gum issues and one fine afternoon i visited partha clinic. I am glad that i did, because i had the pleasure of meeting Dr. Sujatha.  I have been to many dentists over the years. Many of them are certified professionals who are money minded and do not have any sense of patient's well being* *** ** ******** *** ******* ** *** *** **** ****** ********* * **** **** ****  Her calm demenaour and approach make her an ideal healthcare professional leader in her domain. 
FIrst of all she made me at ease despite of having fear in dental settings. She thouroughly inspected and did an extraordinary findings which other dentists over the year failed to notice ****  ***** ***** *** *** ****** ******** * **** **** *** *** ******** ** *****  She clearly explained the findings in layman terms and gave alot of great tips to control the problem. I really felt valued with her as a dental patient, because she doesn't have a egoistic attitude of some medial professionals  who think they are superior and patients are inferior. She spoke professionally and at the same time maintained her friendly approach.
I wish all doctors could learn from Dr. Sujatha  about how to treat patients !!! . I really wish Dr . Sujatha best wishes in her endevours and looking forward to meet her again and definitely recommend her to all my family and acquaintances :)

I had severe tooth pain , could not bear it at all.I met Dr Sujatha at Sparsh hospital.She reduced my pain immediately by starting the root canal treatment.I m very thankful for her painless root canal treatment as I have suffered with same dental pain with another doctor.

I got my decayed teeth treated by Dr.Sujatha.I had fear of dentist but her approach has made me very happy. I'm really satisfied by her treatment. I would definitely recommend her for all my friends and family.She is celebrity dentist who has even come on TV9 in 2017.I had seen her on tv once and after that here again. I'm very happy n thankfull  to mam.

I had to get a routine scaling done for my teeth. The same procedure carried out by different dentists earlier was very painful and didn’t feel right. 
*** ****** ******* ** **** ******* ** *** **** ** **** *** most importantly helped me understand intricacies of dental hygiene. I got laser treatment done too by her for the healthy growth of gum tissues which was absolutely painless. I would recommend Dr. Sujata to anyone with dental pain or issue.

Very pleasant behavior. she has good hands on experience.
Her experience matters much. When she worked on my teeth, i could not feel that anything is going on.

She is the only doctor working. The support staff needs more experience. 
so over all i will give 3.75 out of 5.

Dr Sujatha is extreemly perfect person and humble.she explained me about my problem and proper steps and sitting for my treatment.today their is no pain .she gave me all advise and follow up schedule.I haven't felt like my surgery been done.*** ** ******* ** *** ****** thanx Dr Sujatha.

Exceptional :3

*** ******* ** ** ********* ******** She took the time to explain every procedure she was doing. For example, when I got my teeth infected, Dr. Sujatha was very supportive, and thorough when explaining the process. She is a professional and has a naturally lovely personality. I would recommend Dr. Sujatha to everyone. *** ** *** **** ******* * **** **** ****

**** *** ******* ****** ********* ** *** *****

I can say that myself and everybody who have visited Partha dental clinic, Jayanagar are guaranteed examples of the best and perfect dental treatment in the city.

Dr. Sujatha consulted my wife and she just knew what we wanted and what my wife was lacking due to her irregular and crooked teeth. Dr. Sujatha is very dedicated and friendly, she had corrected my wife's teeth, designed a  very beautiful smile and given back the  lot of confidence which my wife was lacking from so many years. the entire treatment was painless, Transparent and completed in just three working days.
Mu wife got 3M zerconia permanent crowns which looks really natural on her. Thanks to Dr. Sujatha for treating and giving my wife a  new life.

I am very satisfied and happy about everything at Partha dental clinic, Jayanagar
